# @caistech/* consumed from GitHub Packages (canonical property-services SDK, 2026-07-05).
# Token via env GITHUB_PACKAGES_TOKEN — matches this repo's CI convention
# (.github/workflows/ci.yml aliases it from the GH_PACKAGES_TOKEN secret; GitHub
# forbids GITHUB_-prefixed secret names). Set the same var in Vercel (sensitive,
# prod+preview) and it resolves from the shell env for local installs.
@caistech:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_PACKAGES_TOKEN}
